! Trends in Antisemitic Attitudes in United Kingdom<ref>{{cite web|title=Attitudes Toward Jews, Israel and the Palestinian-Israeli Conflict in Ten European Countries – April 2004|url=http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/european_attitudes_april_2004.pdf|publisher=ADL|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407072334/http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/european_attitudes_april_2004.pdf|archive-date=7 April 2014|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Attitudes Toward Jews in Twelve European Countries – May 205|url=http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/european_attitudes_may_2005.pdf|publisher=ADL|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107021940/http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/european_attitudes_may_2005.pdf|archive-date=7 January 2014|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Attitudes Toward Jews and the Middle East in Six European Countries – July 2007|url=http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/European_Attitudes_Survey_July_2007.pdf|publisher=ADL|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203012727/http://archive.adl.org/anti_semitism/european_attitudes_survey_july_2007.pdf|archive-date=3 December 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Attitudes Toward Jews in Seven European Countries – February 2009|url=http://archive.adl.org/Public%20ADL%20Anti-Semitism%20Presentation%20February%202009%20_3_.pdf|publisher=ADL|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407072522/http://archive.adl.org/public%20adl%20anti-semitism%20presentation%20february%202009%20_3_.pdf|archive-date=7 April 2014|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Attitudes Toward Jews in Ten European Countries – March 2012|url=http://archive.adl.org/Anti_semitism/adl_anti-semitism_presentation_february_2012.pdf|publisher=ADL|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512182655/http://archive.adl.org/Anti_se